text: Ścinawka Dolna () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Radków, within Kłodzko County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. It lies approximately east of Radków, north-west of Kłodzko, and south-west of the regional capital Wrocław. == People == * Emanuel Aloys Förster == References == Category:Villages in Kłodzko County
title: Ścinawka Dolna
